section.section:
In determining whether to approve an application by a carrier to change its election, the Commissioner shall consider:
the applicant's financial condition and the financial condition of any parent or guaranteeing corporation;
the applicant's history of assuming and managing risk;
the applicant's commitment to market fairly to all small employers in the State or in the applicant's service area;
the applicant's ability to assume and manage the risk of enrolling groups under this subtitle without the protection of the Pool; and
the effect of approval of the application on the financial viability of the Pool.
